WEBVTT

00:01.672 --> 00:04.011
Previously on "Desperate
Housewives"... Why on earth

00:04.035 --> 00:05.982
would you let them finger paint
before breakfast?

00:06.006 --> 00:08.154
It's my job to clean that up,
so it's my call.

00:08.179 --> 00:10.057
Some households reversed roles.

00:10.081 --> 00:11.458
Let's give this another shot.

00:11.482 --> 00:13.020
Some old flames...

00:13.044 --> 00:14.121
You want me back?

00:14.145 --> 00:15.122
Yeah.

00:15.146 --> 00:16.093
Were put out.

00:16.117 --> 00:17.464
It has to be something
you're ingesting.

00:17.488 --> 00:20.067
Who prepares your meals?

00:20.091 --> 00:22.469
I understand you've been having
some marital problems.

00:22.493 --> 00:25.132
And while some learn
to forgive...

00:25.156 --> 00:27.704
Deirdre got pregnant
before I went to jail.

00:27.728 --> 00:30.177
Zach is your son, isn't he?

00:30.201 --> 00:31.278
Yep.

00:31.302 --> 00:32.409
Wow.

00:32.433 --> 00:34.490
Others could not
bring themselves

00:34.514 --> 00:37.165
to forget their past.

00:44.575 --> 00:47.354
The remarkable thing
about Danny Farrell

00:47.378 --> 00:51.498
was that he had only been
a paperboy for six months,

00:51.522 --> 00:54.361
and in that time,
he had become the enemy

00:54.385 --> 00:56.703
of every woman on Wisteria Lane.

00:56.727 --> 01:01.037
If there was a puddle
on someone's property...

01:01.061 --> 01:03.740
He found it.

01:03.764 --> 01:06.251
If a new rosebush
had just been planted...

01:06.275 --> 01:11.178
He destroyed it.

01:11.202 --> 01:16.253
If a cat was enjoying
a moment in the sun...

01:16.277 --> 01:19.426
He ended it.

01:19.450 --> 01:24.831
People wondered
if Danny would ever change.

01:24.855 --> 01:28.135
They should have
talked to Susan Mayer.

01:28.159 --> 01:31.598
She could have told them...

01:31.622 --> 01:36.603
Obnoxious boys
tend to become obnoxious men,

01:36.627 --> 01:40.307
just like the one...

01:40.331 --> 01:43.201
She had been married to.

01:44.705 --> 01:46.183
Hey!

01:46.207 --> 01:50.687
Carl, I see you.
Just stop right there.

01:50.711 --> 01:52.159
Hey, susie q.

01:52.183 --> 01:54.161
What are you doing?

01:54.185 --> 01:56.193
I'm just gettin' the paper.

01:56.217 --> 01:58.365
That's Edie's paper,
and this is Edie's house.

01:58.389 --> 02:01.198
Do we have to do this now?
I haven't had my coffee yet.

02:01.222 --> 02:04.802
Did you spend the night
with Edie?

02:06.257 --> 02:08.375
Oh, my god.

02:08.399 --> 02:10.336
Susie, just calm down.

02:10.360 --> 02:12.679
You are forbidden
from ever seeing her again.

02:12.703 --> 02:14.681
Do you hear me? Forbidden!

02:14.705 --> 02:17.844
We're divorced. You can't
tell me who I can date.

02:17.868 --> 02:21.688
I live on this street. Your
daughter lives on this street.

02:21.712 --> 02:24.299
I will not have you flaunting
your sexcapades in front of us.

02:24.323 --> 02:25.352
Sexcapades?

02:25.376 --> 02:27.294
Forbidden.

02:27.318 --> 02:30.427
I would love to continue this,
but it's time for breakfast,

02:30.451 --> 02:32.429
and Edie is making me
a frittata.

02:32.453 --> 02:37.233
Oh! Well, I just bet she is.

02:42.693 --> 02:44.676
Mrs. Mayer, I gotta talk to you.

02:44.700 --> 02:46.673
Oh, now is not a good time,
Danny.

02:46.697 --> 02:48.675
You're a month behind
in your payments.

02:48.699 --> 02:50.717
I'll take care of it, I promise.

02:50.741 --> 02:53.180
My dad says, if you read
something and don't pay for it

02:53.204 --> 02:54.887
that's the same as stealing.

02:54.911 --> 02:57.153
Hi, ida. Can we talk
about this later?

02:57.177 --> 02:59.155
I just found out my ex
is dating my neighbor,

02:59.179 --> 03:01.157
and I'm really ticked off.

03:01.181 --> 03:03.660
Save it!
I provide you a service,

03:03.684 --> 03:05.671
and I deserve to be paid
for that service.

03:05.695 --> 03:08.235
Yes, the women of Wisteria Lane

03:08.259 --> 03:11.568
believe Danny Farrell
to be the enemy.

03:11.592 --> 03:13.522
Deadbeat!

03:17.728 --> 03:19.175
They also believed

03:19.199 --> 03:21.348
the enemy of my enemy

03:21.372 --> 03:23.802
is my friend.

